	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I didn't rout the audio through an expansion port pin because my T89 adapter didn't have the middle pins on the card edge. I had to use a wire. Otherwise I would have routed it through an expansion port pin. I considered purchasing an adapter that did have the middle pins, but I didn't want to spend what they were selling it for at the time when I already had an adapter handy.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


